<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>SOLDIERS OF CHIRST</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Krista sepaihte haw,
 Kigal ging zing unla;
 * Pathien hatna suongin ding un,
 A kumawt cha zalin (3)

[V2]
 2. Lalpa vang a hatin,
 A hih theihna muongun;
 * Kuole Isu hatna muong chuh,
 Zinmang sangin a hat. (3)

[V3]
 3. Mun cheng veng phau unla,
 Thagau chau lo hielin;
 * Hehpih leh thilbawl theihna chun,
 Khawvel pumpi zo un. (3)

[V4]
 4. Buoina hungum mahleh,
 Na zawh vek tieng uleh;
 * Krista vangin nuom un natin,
 Tawp chanin ding un lau. (3)

[V5]
 5. Hatna leh lawpna chun,
 Do unla, pang zel un;
 * Thim thilhih theihna haw cheng chuh,
 Na zawh niu tung ina. (3)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>318</hymn_number>
</song>